        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Religious Exemptions for Social Security and Healthcare Taxes Act</strong></p> <p>This bill allows taxpayers who have a religious objection to participation in the Social Security system a credit or refund of employment taxes deducted to fund benefits under such system.</p>]]>
        </text>
